casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Cooke, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Cooke, 120 Ohio St.3d 356, 2008-Ohio-6321.]

(No. 2008-0522 Submitted October 14, 2008 Decided December 11, 2008.) Robin N. Piper, Butler County Prosecuting Attorney, and Daniel G. Eichel, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The cause is remanded to the court of appeals for further consideration in view of our opinion in State v. Kalish, 120 Ohio St.3d 23, 2008-Ohio-4912, 896 N.E.2d 124.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur. Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents. *357Charles M. Conliff, for appellant.
